{"tid":555590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街萬寧當我乞衣呀？！","createTime":"2018-02-09T15:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T16:12:06.000Z","uid":87337,"like":42,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7fed927782016b85ddbfaf6dae3f5376ea76949","tid":555590,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:09:15.000Z","msg":"屌你老母on撚9<br />\n岩岩陪呀媽去萬寧買野<br />\n佢問我有冇儲分 我話冇 佢就話我明明比咗張你做咩唔用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我又唔係成撚日走去買野<br />\n於是我就問佢啲分有咩用<br />\n原來我老母都唔知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 老母<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 萬寧收銀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔該我想問張卡宜家有幾多分？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：247分<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁可以換到啲咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：儲夠1000分換到一張20$券<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我心諗 幾撚時先儲到1000分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁幾錢儲到一分？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：每5蚊儲到一分<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買5$先得1分<br />\n儲夠1000分有20蚊<br />\n即係我買咗5000$先得20$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當我乞衣呀？屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n計返折扣既話即係 99.6折<br />\n<br />\n我真係多撚謝哂你呀萬寧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個積分卡咁撚寒酸<br />\n講出黎都唔好意思啦係咪呀<br />\n咁唔想亳比啲客咪唔撚好搞呢啲19積分制囉<br />\n咁撚大間公司做埋啲咁垃圾既積分制真係好撚寒酸呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb29f218cea194b602c51b5fbc3b3f4ab3eaf870","tid":555590,"uid":87337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"仲要之前去親萬寧都比人當賊咁昅實哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好撚無癮"},{"pid":"e607a432ec9386ebcbd810aeb4693b567f2c9de1","tid":555590,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:24:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過認真儲呢啲分？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd37151b6d6a00d374fea0f87dc578ff6a63cf27","tid":555590,"uid":50780,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"啲表情符號終於有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec80a172dbfb0558344528572c5032c54ca0aae8","tid":555590,"uid":693,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:26:15.000Z","msg":"屌你仲去買野你話你係唔係犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7047d9cca7d921a9d54f968c1862780f87d63cb7","tid":555590,"uid":87337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲表情符號終於有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e99dd431b1a11455d0a8f4665369408eee7d49","tid":555590,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T15:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你仲去買野你話你係唔係犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>